<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1986—<ref href="/us/pl/99/514">Pub. L. 99–514</ref>, as amended by <ref href="/us/pl/100/647/s1017/c/12">Pub. L. 100–647, § 1017(c)(12)</ref>, substituted “6427(j)(2)” for “6427(i)(2)”.</p>
